title: Reminder: Trick or Treat Night is October 31st, 2015! (City of Elyria, OH)
text: ( Source : City of Elyria, OH ) Trick or Treat Night in the City of Elyria will be Halloween night, October 31 , 2015 from 6:00-7:30pm! The Annual Kiwanis Halloween Parade will be this coming Sunday, October 25th . Lineup for the parade begins
